room_title: Escape room "Naughty or Nice" by Memphis Escape Rooms in Memphis
room_description:
Another year has flown by, and the holiday season is upon us once again! But things are not merry and bright for all, because this year despite your best efforts, you’ve found yourself firmly on the naughty list! 

There may be a bit of Christmas magic yet, as Santa has given you another chance to prove yourself and get your name moved to the nice side of the list. 

With Christmas Eve fast approaching, Santa and the Elves have fallen off the pace, and fear that they may not have everything ready to go in time. The Big Guy has recruited your team to help out as they rapidly approach crunch time. 
​
Can you move your name to the nice list and get Christmas back on track, or will you spend this holiday season on the naughty list?
